                            <comment id="278201" author="joe.grund" created="Thu, 27 Aug 2020 14:20:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Concern here is what happens to snapshot commands if one of the lustre targets cannot be found due to it being mounted on a different node than what&apos;s listed in primary / failover. This appears possible for everything besides the MGS which is currently constrained to two VMS.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
